This README file contains information on the contents of the
meta-backport-kirkstone layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

  URI: https://git.yoctoproject.org/poky/meta
  branch: kirkstone

  URI: https://github.com/rauc/meta-rauc
  branch: kirkstone

  URI: https://git.yoctoproject.org/meta-raspberrypi
  branch: kirkstone

  URI: https://github.com/rauc/meta-rauc-community
  branch: kirkstone

  URI: https://github.com/gportay/meta-downstream
  path: meta-rauc-raspberrypi-firmware
  branch: kirkstone

Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the meta-backport-kirkstone layer via the
repository pull requests (https://github.com/gportay/meta-downstream/pulls).

Bugs
====

Please report any bugs against the meta-backport-kirkstone layer via the
repository issues (https://github.com/gportay/meta-downstream/issues).

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-backport-kirkstone layer to your build
 II. Building the firmware

I. Adding the meta-backport-kirkstone layer to your build
=========================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-backport-kirkstone'

II. Building the firmware
=========================

Run 'bitbake core-image-minimal'
